  <brief_title>Validation of Phase Lag Entropy(PLE) as an Indicator of Depth of Sedation in Patients Undergoing Spinal Anesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Validation of Phase Lag Entropy(PLE) as an Indicator of Depth of Sedation in Patients Undergoing Spinal Anesthesia: Comparative Analysis With Bispectral Index</official_title>
