  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      For verifying the phase lag entropy as the tool for measurement of level of consciousness,
      the investigators compared phase lag entropy to bispectral index. Using Target-Controlled
      Infusion pump, propofol was infused for sedation during the spinal anesthesia. The
      investigators measured Observer's Assessment of Alertness/Sedation Scale as the propofol
      concentration rises. At the same time, The investigators observed phase lag entropy score and
      bispectral index score.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
